================================================================================
AI-assisted authoring
================================================================================

Portions of the source code, configuration, evaluation scripts, and
documentation in this repository were drafted with the assistance of large
language models. All output was reviewed and accepted by Adam Rahman, who
takes responsibility for the resulting code, claims, and reproducibility
guarantees made by this project.

The model weights distributed with this repository (and on the matching
Hugging Face model card) are a fine-tune of IBM-ESA TerraMind 1.0 trained
on AMD Instinct MI300X. The fine-tuning procedure is documented in
docs/TRAINING.md. No model weights, checkpoints, or training data were
generated by an AI assistant.
